data.description: “TAKE MY RATE 3.75%” Exciting Opportunity for First-Time or Seasoned Home Buyers, and Empty Nesters!   1 Year Home Warranty- AHS  Cosmetically Appealing Property Ready for Sale!  Marvelous Ranch House:  Welcome to this charming ranch house that's ready for you to make your mark. This property offers a cozy atmosphere and a versatile layout, just waiting for your personal touch. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a canvas for your creativity, this home is an absolute gem.  In Need of Some Cosmetic Repairs  Above-Ground Pool: Imagine relaxing and unwinding in your very own above-ground pool. It's the perfect spot for enjoying sunny days and hosting memorable pool gatherings with friends and family. This feature is sure to enhance your backyard oasis.  Expansive Fenced Backyard: Calling all gardening enthusiasts and nature lovers! This property boasts a large, fenced backyard, ready for your landscaping dreams to come to life. Grow your own fruits and vegetables, cultivate a fragrant flower garden, or create a serene haven where you can reconnect with nature. The property line goes beyond the fence to the creek.  Play Area for Kids: For parents, there's a dedicated play area within the spacious backyard. Your little ones can swing, slide, and let their imaginations run wild, all while you enjoy a moment of relaxation. This delightful feature will keep the kids entertained for hours.  Entertainment Area: If you love hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories with loved ones, this property features an impressive entertainment area. Picture the laughter, clinking glasses, and the aroma of delicious food drifting through the air. It's an ideal space for making cherished moments.  This exceptional property combines functionality, potential, and a promising future. Whether you're a first-time home buyer eager to have a place to call your own or an empty nester seeking a property to enjoy your golden years, this house is brimming with potential.
